    "def": "The twenty-third Baron von Drax, principal stockholder and CEO of the Grendel International Corporation. A heavy florid man in bespoke burgundy who carries the conviction of a bloodline bred for war. He has personally contributed the human DNA spliced into the Deinonychus draxi line."
